dent, riot, war, government intervention, embargoes, strikes, labour difficulties or strikes, equipment failure, or any other causes beyond our control.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">21.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">We shall under no circumstances be liable for any loss (whether direct or indirect) of revenue, loss of profit or any indirect or consequential loss whatsoever suffered, sustained or incurred by you or by other person arising (directly or indirectly) out of or relating to the Service.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">22.&nbsp;T</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">he Company reserve the rights to modify, from time to time, all or any of the provisions under these Terms and Conditions.&nbsp; Please refer to NEXSTGO official website for the updated warranty policy and other applicable terms:&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.nexstgo.com/\">http://www.nexstgo.com</a></span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">23.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">The Terms and Conditions shall be governed by the laws of the Republic of Singapore and the Customer and We agree to submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the Singapore courts.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">24.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Should there be any inconsistency between Chinese and English versions, the English version shall prevail.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Asian District Maintenance Plan</strong></p>\r\n<p>*Regions include: Hong Kong, China, Macau, Taiwan, Singapore and Malaysia</p>\r\n<p>1. Asian District Maintenance Plan enables customers who travel with, or relocate Avita laptop to receive warranty service in any region where their product is announced and sold and supported by Nexstgo or a Nexstgo authorized reseller under Nexstgo Computer Limited Warranty and/or the destination region Warranty Services Agreement.</p>\r\n<p>2. The length of Asian District Maintenance Plan is based upon the original warranty period assigned in the region of origin where the laptop was first sold by Nexstgo or a Nexstgo authorized reseller.</p>\r\n<p>3. The phone support languages and the method of service will be determined by the destination region. For customers who have on-site repair warranty, on-site service will be delivered where it is available.</p>\r\n<p>4. Some service and/or parts may not be available in all regions. Nexstgo or a Nexstgo authorized reseller may repair the laptop with comparable Avita parts. For example, if the product was purchased with a Japanese keyboard, and service request is submitted in US, Nexstgo may replace with a US keyboard upon your agreement.</p>\r\n<p>5. Some regions may have fees and restrictions that apply at the time of service such as packaging, shipping and handling fees. You will be advised of your responsibility to pay these fees at the time of service.</p>\r\n<p>6. For Avita products, if a customer has purchased warranty extension in the original region of hardware purchase to extend the Nexstgo base warranty offered with a product, Asian District Maintenance Plan will provide coverage until the end of purchased warranty extension.</p>','sg','2017-11-30 15:11:30','2018-11-02 09:18:47'),(4,'tc','維修條款及細則 (TW)','<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; margin-left: 18.0pt; mso-para-margin-left: 0gd; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>保固期內，台灣力高創科有限公司（以下稱「<span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>」或「維修中心」）遵從維修服務條款及細則及產品有限硬體保固條款及細則為<span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>有關產品提供免費維修服務。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>保修服務僅適用於您購買產品的國家。<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">(包括在\"</span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">亞洲區尊尚保養計劃\"的地區除外。)</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>保固期內，若違反任何維修服務條款及細則，產品均不在保固範圍之內，維修中心將按故障情況另行報價或不提供維修服務。用戶自行維修產品、產品主機或配件入水、人為損壞、機殼／表面損毀、未依說明書使用產品及將產品更改使用均被視為違反維修服務條款及細則。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>所有保固期外、保固標籤損毀之產品或非該地區所銷售之貨品<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (</span>例如<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>平行進口之貨品<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>、保固期外或任何產品辨認標貼損毀或缺失之產品及在違反維修服務條款及細則的情況下，除所需之零件費用外，用戶需先付服務費，此費用並不予發還。維修中心將在適當的時候通過電話或書面形式通知客戶正式報價。 所有費用必須全額支付。保固期外，如產品已經停止銷售，沒有零件可以維修，維修中心並有權拒絕維修此產品。維修中心有權以相同產品、產品升級或折扣優惠替代產品維修，費用必須由用戶全額支付。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>享用產品保修服務，客戶必須在指定經銷商購買產品及出示機身序號或有效銷售發票正本<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>發票必須清楚顯示經銷商的名稱、購買日期、發票編號、產品型號、機身編號<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (</span>適用之產品<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>、產品價格並蓋上經銷商的印章；手寫發票必須附上機盒內的型號編碼及機身編號貼紙，方可享用產品保修服務。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>未能出示有效銷售發票正本或機身序號之產品將被視為非保修產品處理。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>將為經維修中心於完成維修後維修後更換之零件提供<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>天免費保固服務（限於在正常使用情況下相同的零件和<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>或機械缺陷）您將得到相同硬體保修的餘額或額外三十日（<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>）之保修服務，以較長者為準。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">8.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>所更換損壞之零件，包括但不限於硬碟和記憶體之零件恕不退回。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">9.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span>維修中心對由於與客戶溝通失敗造成的延誤概不負責。中心提供有效的聯繫電話號碼和<span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span>或電子郵件地址。 如果客戶維修後一（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）週內沒有收到通知，請通過電話聯繫維修中心。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">10.&nbsp;</span>客戶需在維修中心通知取件日期開始計三個月內取回產品，否則用戶產品如有損壞、遺失等情況，維修中心概不承擔任何責任。如用戶六（<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>）個月內還未取回產品，維修中心有權自行處置該產品，恕不另行通知和賠償。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">11.&nbsp;</span>請妥善保管維修單據，憑單取件，若被他人冒領，維修中心概不承擔任何責任。如未能提供該單據，維修中心有權拒絕退回產品。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">12.&nbsp;</span>客戶有責任為產品中所有用戶程式和數據備份。<span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>不對任何軟體，程式或數據或文件的丟失，更改或損壞負責。 所有交付給維修中心之產品，如果客戶在發出維修通知後要求退回，維修中心應當按照規定將產品退回給客戶（包括維修報價如適用）。產品將以當前現狀退回給客戶。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">13.&nbsp;</span>如維修中心在維修非保固產品期間發現用戶違反任何維修服務條款及細則<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (</span>包括但不限於自行維修、產品主機或配件入水、人為損壞<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>，維修中心有權取消定額維俢報價，並按故障情況向客戶重新報價。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">14.&nbsp;</span>維修中心有權拒絕有關維修服務的書面或非書面報告的不合理要求。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">15.&nbsp;</span>維修中心的維修服務只適用於產品硬體。除另有規定外，配件如耳機、電腦連接線、電源線、雷射光碟片等將不包括在維修服務內。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">16.&nbsp;</span>電子產品中所有內存資料有可能於維修後遺失或刪除。用戶將產品送修前，請自行及自費（如適用的話）預先製作一份獨立的資料複本，並取消任何密碼。用戶同意和明白在維修期間，產品上的所有資料都有可能會被刪除或改動，用戶對此不會異議。對於儲存在產品上的任何資料發生遺失、更動、刪除或無法存取的問題，維修中心概不負責，也不承擔任何責任。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">17.&nbsp;</span>維修中心不會保證任何產品在維俢後不會出現作業中斷或作業錯誤的問題，也沒有確保任何產品在所有的作業環境下都能得到支援的義務，包括但不限於與所有軟硬體及其將來版本的相容性問題，客戶確認並無任何異議。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">18.&nbsp;</span>有限保固並不包括非<span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>之硬體、軟體及配件。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">19.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>擁有對上述的條款及細則之最終裁決權及解釋權。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">20.&nbsp;</span>不可抗力：<span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>對於天災，火災，水災，事故，騷亂，戰爭，政府介入，禁運，罷工，勞工困難或罷工，設備故障等造成的任何延誤或失敗或其他任何超出我們控制的原因不承擔任何責任。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">21.&nbsp;</span>在任何情況下，我們都不承擔由於您或其他人或與服務有關（直接或間接）。或因以下原因（直接或間接）而遭受，支付或招致的收入，利潤損失或任何間接或相應的損失（不論直接或間接）。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">22.&nbsp;</span>本公司保留隨時修改上述條款及細則的權利。請瀏覽<span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO</span>網頁查看最新產品保固資料及其他適用條款<span lang=\"EN-US\">: </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.nexstgo.com/\">http://www.nexstgo.com</a></span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">23.&nbsp;</span>條款和條件受臺灣法律的管轄，我們和客戶同意服從臺灣臺北地方法院的專屬管轄權。</p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">24.&nbsp;</span>英文版本與中文版本倘出現任何抵觸或不相符之處，概以英文版本為準。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span lang=\"ZH-TW\">亞洲區尊尚保養計劃</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>*<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">地區包括</span>: <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">香港</span>, <span lang=\"ZH-HK\">中國</span>, <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">澳門</span>, <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">台灣</span>, <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">星加坡和馬來西亞</span></p>\r\n<p>1. <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">亞洲區尊尚保養計劃使攜帶或重新定居任何符合資格的</span>Avita<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">筆記本電腦的客戶能夠在</span>Nexstgo<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">或</span>Nexstgo<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">授權經銷商根據</span>Nexstgo Computer Limited<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">保固公佈並銷售其產品的任何地區獲得保固服務</span> <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">和</span>/<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">或目的地地區保固服務協議。</span></p>\r\n<p>2. <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">亞洲區尊尚保養計劃的長度基於</span>Nexstgo<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">或</span>Nexstgo<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">授權經銷商首次銷售筆記本電腦的原有地區指定的原有的保固期。</span></p>\r\n<p>3. <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">電話支持語言和服務方法將由目的地地區確定。</span> <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">對於具有到府維修服務的客戶，將可在有提供到府維修服務的地區得到相同的服務。</span></p>\r\n<p>4. <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">某些服務和</span>/<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">或部件可能並非在所有地區都可提供。</span> Nexstgo<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">或</span>Nexstgo<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">授權經銷商可以使用可的</span>Avita <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">部件修理。</span> <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">例如，如果購買的產品是使用日語鍵盤，並且服務請求是在美國提交的，則</span>Nexstgo<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">可能會在您同意後使用美國鍵盤替換。</span></p>\r\n<p>5. <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">某些地區可能會收取費用和提供有限制的服務，例如包裝，運輸和手續費。</span> <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">您將被告知您有責任在提供服務時支付這些費用。</span></p>\r\n<p>6. <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">對於</span>Avita<span lang=\"ZH-TW\">產品，如果客戶在原本購買地區購買了由</span>Nexstgo <span lang=\"ZH-TW\">提供的延期保固以擴展產品的基本保固，則亞洲區尊尚保養計劃將提供保固服務直至購買的保固延期結束。</span></p>','tw','2017-12-06 13:45:14','2018-11-02 10:26:12'),(5,'en','Repair T&C (MY)','<p>&nbsp;<!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">During the warranty period, the free-of-charge repair service for official Products of</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> Nexstgo Company Limited</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> (&ldquo;NEXSTGO&rdquo; or &ldquo;Repair Service Centre&rdquo;) shall be offered and subjected to these Repair Service Terms and Conditions and Limited Warranty Terms and Conditions.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">The NEXSTGO warranty service is applicable only in the country where you purchased your product.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">During the warranty period, no free of charge repair service shall be provided in the event of violation of any Repair Service Terms and Conditions. In this case repair charges shall be separately quoted by the Repair Service Centre or no repair service will be provided. Any self-repairs, damage done to the product or its accessories due to exposure to water, damage caused by misuse, </span>cabinets/cosmetic damage, <span lang=\"EN-US\">use in violation of instructions and alternation shall be considered as a violation of Repair Service Terms and Conditions.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">In addition to the necessary spare parts charges, a non-refundable service fee will be imposed in advance to all non-official products (i.e. parallel imports), out-of-warranty products, products with broken or missing identification label or where any violation of Repair Service Terms and Conditions being occurred. Repair Service Centre will inform the customer of an official quotation by phone or in writing in due course. All charges must be paid in full. We reserve the right to refuse repair service to end-of-life products or when parts become unavailable.&nbsp; For out-of-warranty products, Repair Service Center shall have the right to provide the same product, product upgrade or product discount to substitute product repair, and all charges must be paid in full by customer.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Customer can enjoy warranty service provided that the products are purchased from authorized dealers and customer is required to present the original proof of purchase, which shall contain the full name of the dealer, date of purchase, invoice number, product model number, serial number (for applicable products), product price and dealer&rsquo;s company chop.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">If the customer fails to present the original proof of purchase, the products will be treated as non-warranty products.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NEXSTGO shall provide a one (1) month post-service warranty for the same serviced part (limited to same electrical and/or mechanical defect(s) under normal usage). You receive either the balance of your original hardware warranty or thirty calendar (30) days, whichever is longer.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">All changed defective parts, including but not limited to hard disk drive and memory, are non-returnable.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">9.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Repair Service Centre shall not be responsible for any delay caused by the failure of communication with the customer. Customer is required to provide Repair Service Centre with valid contact number(s) and/or email address. If customer does not receive any pick up notification one (1) week after the drop off date, please contact Repair Service Centre by phone.</span></p>\r\n<p><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">10.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Customer shall collect their product(s) within three (3) months after receipt of pick up notification from Repair Service Centre. Repair Service Cen