font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-HK\" style=\"line-height: 106%; color: #525252;\">the serial number has been altered, effaced or removed;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; color: #525252;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -19.5pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #525252;\">11.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #525252;\">NEXSTGO may use parts or products that are new or refurbished and equivalent to new in performance and reliability in servicing your product.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; color: #525252;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -19.5pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #525252;\">12.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-HK\" style=\"color: #525252;\">Any detective part which has been replaced, shall be NEXSTGO\'s property.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -15.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 36.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; color: #525252;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -19.5pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #525252;\">13.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-HK\" style=\"color: #525252;\">Customer should backup his/her own hard disk contents of his/her own accord before repair. NEXSTGO shall not provide hard disk backup service.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -15.0pt; line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 36.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; color: #525252;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -19.5pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #525252;\">14.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-HK\" style=\"color: #525252;\">In case of repair, hard disk content may be destroyed and customer will not be informed in advance.&nbsp;NEXSTGO shall not be liable for any data, records or program lost due to repair.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; color: #525252;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">15.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #525252;\">Please refer to the Repair Terms and Conditions for the details on the Repair Services.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>'),(26,10,'tc','<p>-</p>'),(27,10,'sc','<p>-</p>'),(28,10,'th','<p>-</p>'),(29,10,'vn','<p>-</p>'),(30,10,'id','<p>-</p>'),(31,11,'en','<p>-</p>'),(32,11,'tc','<p>-</p>'),(33,11,'sc','<p>力高创科有限公司 (下称 &ldquo;NEXSTGO&rdquo;)</p>\r\n<p>保固条款</p>\r\n<p>AVITA笔记型电脑有限硬体保固 (只适用于AVITA系列)</p>\r\n<p>1. NEXSTGO为客户提供18个月免费自携和到府收送维修服务 (包括人工及零件费) 。</p>\r\n<p>2. 本保固条款包括18个月电池保固服务 (由发票注明购买曰起计)。</p>\r\n<p>3. 本保固条款包括18个月变压器保固服务 (由发票注明购买曰起计)。</p>\r\n<p>4. 笔记型电脑于发票日起15日内经维修中心确认含LCD萤幕坏点情况(展示品除外)，按以下标准，若坏点总数多于五颗，包装及配件完整、凭发票可向原购买经销商更换新品。</p>\r\n<p>5. 笔记型电脑于发票日起15日内经维修中心确认含硬体故障者(展示品除外)、包装及配件完整、凭发票可向原购买经销商更换新品。</p>\r\n<p>6. 客户要求保修服务时，必须先向NEXSTGO服务员出示购买电脑之正本单据(或机身序号)，影印或传真副本恕不受理。倘未能出示，客户需缴付维修费用。如客户无法提供购买电脑之正本单据(或机身序号)，NEXSTGO有权拒绝向客户提供服务。</p>\r\n<p>7. 客户自携保修服务，如客户要求运送及收回电脑，客户需负责所需运送费用。</p>\r\n<p>8. 本保固只包括硬体保修服务。一切配置及附件，如软体、电脑连接线、电源线、光碟、及用户指南等均不包括在保固服务内。</p>\r\n<p>9. NEXSTGO不负责重装预载之软体。倘客户要求重装预载软体服务，需向NEXSTGO缴付服务费用。</p>\r\n<p>10. 本保固服务只供予经NEXSTGO技术员判断为正常运作下损坏，倘由于以下事故引致电脑失效，NEXSTGO概不负责如下:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;i. 若产品故障是因为任何损坏或意外损坏，机壳／表面损毁，不适当使用或滥用，液体侵入或浸没，疏忽，误用，未经授权的修改，极端的环境，极端的物理或电器外力或干扰，电力供应，雷电，静电，火灾，不可抗力的因素或其他外在原因;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ii. 若电脑，包括软体及硬体，曾被非本公司之技术人员改装、处理及/或维修;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;iii. 若附于产品上的产品编号曾被删改或除去;</p>\r\n<p>11. NEXSTGO可能使用性能和可靠性等同于全新或翻新的部件或产品维修客户的产品。</p>\r\n<p>12. 已更换损坏之零件乃属NEXSTGO所有。</p>\r\n<p>13. 客户在维修前，需自行将电脑内之内容储存备份。 NEXSTGO并不提供备份服务。</p>\r\n<p>14. 于维修时，电脑之内容可能被删除，NEXSTGO将不会预先通知客户，对于引致资料或程式之损失，NEXSTGO一概恕不负责。</p>\r\n<p>15. 有关维修服务的详情，请参阅维修条款及细则。</p>'),(34,11,'th','<p>-</p>'),(35,11,'vn','<p>-</p>'),(36,11,'id','<p>-</p>'),(37,12,'en','<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"color: #525252;\">Nexstgo Company Limited (&ldquo;NEXSTGO&rdquo;) Limited Warranty for AVITA Notebook Computer Devices (Only applicable to &ldquo;AVITA&rdquo; series)</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -19.5pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: #525252;\">1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-HK\" style=\"color: #525252;\">NEXSTGO provides limited warranty period, eighteen (18) months, for customer who has free carry-in repair service, including parts and labour for the notebook computer.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -19.5pt; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -19.5pt; line-height: 106%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0cm 0cm .0001pt 37.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 106%; color: #525252;\">2.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font